{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2062", "repo": "rails", "body": "Yeah, this problem can be fixed on an adapter level. But the fix is not very pretty. Here how I had to monkey patch MSSQL adapter:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nx.projections.map! do |p|\r\n   p == \"1\" ? Nodes::SqlLiteral.new(\"#{p} as _fld_#{p}\") : p\r\nend\r\n```\r\nThat is why I thought fixing the root of the problem would be a better idea. ", "_id": {"$oid": "523848dbbd3543c1510111b9"}, "issue_id": 2062, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1787118", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2062#issuecomment-1787118", "updated_at": "2011-08-11T23:58:19Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk", "login": "arkadiyk", "gravatar_id": "1e765e9ed7b03eefa822069f0af836ef", "html_url": "https://github.com/arkadiyk", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1e765e9ed7b03eefa822069f0af836ef?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ff00a4b6b7d31066eda80cc1d85f81677.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 222976, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/arkadiyk/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-08-11T23:58:19Z", "id": 1787118, "owner": "rails"}
